---
import SectionInner from "@/components/ui/Astro/SectionInner.astro";
---

<section class="px-8 py-28 max-lg:py-20 max-sm:px-5 relative bg-accent-bg text-card">
  <SectionInner>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] gap-16 items-start max-lg:grid-cols-1 max-lg:gap-8">
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up duration-[800ms] delay-[100ms]">
        <span class="font-display text-sm tracking-wider block mb-3 text-accent">02</span>
        <h2
          class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-card mb-12"
        >
          Why it matters
        </h2>
        <p
          class="font-display text-[clamp(1.25rem,2vw,1.5rem)] leading-relaxed text-[rgba(250,249,246,0.95)] mb-6"
        >
          Most tools want to manage your life. We only want to hold your today&rsquo;s thoughts so
          you can focus on doing them, not organizing them.
        </p>
        <p
          class="font-body text-base font-light leading-relaxed text-[rgba(250,249,246,0.65)] mb-4"
        >
          The best ideas arrive unannounced. The most important tasks rarely have a deadline.
          todo-app is a single page for a single day &mdash; a scratchpad for the things that matter
          before they slip into tomorrow&rsquo;s regret.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-base font-light leading-relaxed text-[rgba(250,249,246,0.65)]">
          Close it when you&rsquo;re done. Open it when you need it. Nothing more.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex items-center justify-center pt-8 animate-fade-in-up duration-[800ms] delay-[300ms]"
      >
        <blockquote class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-[rgba(250,249,246,0.15)] max-lg:pl-6">
          <p class="font-body text-[1.1rem] italic leading-relaxed text-[rgba(250,249,246,0.8)]">
            The list you make in the morning is a letter to your future self. Write it kindly.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionInner>
</section>

<style>
  blockquote::before {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(250, 249, 246, 0.15);
    content: "\201C";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    blockquote::before {
      left: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
